metadata.name: TIALS.World Computer #2
metadata.description: TIALS.World is the sustainable fashion hub in web3 where you can connect, network and thrive! The Membership NFT collection will serve as a membership pass into TIALS.World and will allow access to mint our upcoming PFP designer collections which will unlock co-creation, phygital fashion, added utilities and access to our launchpad to get funding or launch your next big fashion move! Join our sustainable fashion hub in web3 to start your journey: https://www.discord.gg/tialsworld
